rows.label: qst202208_msg001
rows.name: Excuse me, can I ask you something?

rows.label: qst202208_msg005
rows.name:
N-n-no! Not touch buzzy-buzzy!
Hate buzzy-buzzy!

rows.label: qst202208_msg006
rows.name:
Oh, don't worry! I'm not gonna zap
you, I just wanted to-

rows.label: qst202208_msg007
rows.name:
Mo-mo? ...No! Not come any closer!
Keep buzzy-buzzy away!

rows.label: qst202208_msg008
rows.name:
I think we should probably ask
someone else...

rows.label: qst202208_msg010
rows.name: Don't let it bother you, Raiko.

rows.label: qst202208_msg011
rows.name:
We're sure to find someone who'll
understand the efforts you went to
eventually.
